626
00:51:45.904 --> 00:51:48.289
Lisbeth, entra.

627
00:51:58.398 --> 00:52:00.398
- Ti piace?
- Si', carina.


628
00:52:00.426 --> 00:52:02.426
Ti ringrazio.

629
00:52:03.422 --> 00:52:06.312
- A cosa ti servono i soldi?
